snippet.title: Judge Has Officially Sentenced Amber Heard In US Court...
snippet.description:
Judge Has Officially Sentenced Amber Heard In US Court...
The court case going on between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp continues to wage on despite the fact that most people just want it to end for one reason or another. But, it is not, and as such, more news and details about what is going on with them continues to rage. In recent times, Johnny Depp has been trying to get more information admitted for his case against Amber, including the potential for her being tried for perjury, and Amber is trying to get the case against her dismissed officially in court. We'll break down all the latest for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the latest and "greatest" from the court case with Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. Do you think that anything that these two are doing in court are going to make a difference in the long run? What are you hoping happens next with all that is going on? Or do you just want it to end? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
